{"tid":975842,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"NVIDIA CEO：“It’s underwhelming.”","createTime":"2019-01-10T03:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T02:08:05.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3c291504bdadb8eeea7c9d0d5028c7ad55a68a6a","tid":975842,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:39:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pcworld.com/article/3332025/computers/nvidia-disses-the-radeon-vii-vowing-the-rtx-2080-will-crush-amds-underwhelming-gpu.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcworld.com%2Farticle%2F3332025%2Fcomputers%2Fnvidia-disses-the-radeon-vii-vowing-the-rtx-2080-will-crush-amds-underwhelming-gpu.html&d=XYjAR2kfDNRlBgPoxB6BaI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=5a9e7bd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcworld.com/article/3332025/computers/nvidia-disses-the-radeon-vii-vowing-the-rtx-2080-will-crush-amds-underwhelming-gpu.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog.wongcw.com/2019/01/10/黃仁勳點評7nm-radeon-vii平淡、沒有光追：amd回應/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.wongcw.com%2F2019%2F01%2F10%2F%E9%BB%83%E4%BB%81%E5%8B%B3%E9%BB%9E%E8%A9%957nm-radeon-vii%E5%B9%B3%E6%B7%A1%E3%80%81%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E5%85%89%E8%BF%BD%EF%BC%9Aamd%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%2F&d=XYjAR2kfDNRlBgPoxB6BaI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=58ad9c77\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.wongcw.com/2019/01/10/黃仁勳點評7nm-radeon-vii平淡、沒有光追：amd回應/</a><br />\n<br />\nAMD CEO 蘇姿豐博士在 CES 2019 上正式對外發布 AMD 首款、也是全球首款基於 7nm 工藝的遊戲顯示卡，Radeon VII（Radeon 7）。Radeon VII 內建3840 顆流處理器、加速頻率 1.8GHz、16GB HBM2 VRAM、單精度 13.8TFlops、699 美元、2月7日開賣，官方標榜效能上比 Vega 64 提升 25~42%。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/files/Elvis/News/20180109-AMD/RadeonVII.jpg?versionId=MgonbOQZFWJ4UTU5309smO0yrstBlY6G\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Ffiles%2FElvis%2FNews%2F20180109-AMD%2FRadeonVII.jpg%3FversionId%3DMgonbOQZFWJ4UTU5309smO0yrstBlY6G&h=acca3743&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n對於這款顯示卡，NVIDIA CEO 黃仁勳在 CES 記者會上與媒體交流時被要求點評，他直言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &ldquo;It&rsquo;s underwhelming（平淡的產品）&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n黃仁勳指 Radeon VII 效能糟糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、沒有新意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、沒有光追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、沒有AI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。即使用了 7nm 和 HBM，才勉強追上 RTX 2080<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，然而當 RTX 2080 在遊戲中開啟 DLSS 後就幹翻它，開啟光追後同樣幹翻它。<br />\n<br />\n這還不罷休，黃仁勳總結「一次奇怪的發布，也許 AMD 的人今天起床也是這麼想的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」儘管他最後自嘲了一番，可是話已出口，覆水難收。"},{"pid":"524a4ae392fdd4f620bb99acbf3682e690b6f0e1","tid":975842,"uid":81113,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:42:24.000Z","msg":"我相信好多人都會支持AMD(口講)，然後去買N記"},{"pid":"47221020cce50f88e0119ee6d26942ffe2cac584","tid":975842,"uid":55712,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:45:07.000Z","msg":"開啟光追後同樣幹翻它<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859c06687b67c4c18369bdcb65947dd36a8f4d1e","tid":975842,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T03:45:31.000Z","msg":"有趣的是，隨後在 AMD 的訪談中，記者趁機向 AMD CEO 蘇姿豐詢問對 NVIDIA CEO 黃仁勳點評的看法，她表示「我想說的是，對 Radeon VII 的發布很興奮。我猜想，對方應該還沒有見過這張卡」，也就是暗示黃仁勳是在胡說八道。<br />\n<br />\n另外，蘇姿豐強調，光線追踪是重要的技術，AMD同樣會在硬件和軟件層面上開發。"},{"pid":"582c5a28225b8933ea7ebb8191af942a7ee14568","tid":975842,"uid":31961,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"859c0668